short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A extension that help filters your SOAPUI request to exactly what you need

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Extension help users that use SOAPUI specifically. It allows you to take the default request for any SOAPUI request and then filter it down to the templated BP's you need.
